<h2 class="blog--title">
<a href="/blog/2005/05/23/spring-web-flow-pr3-released">Spring Web Flow PR3 Released</a>
</h2>
<header class="meta-data--container">
<div class="meta-data--item desktop-only">
<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon releases"></div>
<a class="category" href="/blog/category/releases">Releases</a>
</div>
<div class="meta-data--item">
<img class="meta-data--icon" src="null?s=20&amp;d=mm" />
<span class="author">Colin Sampaleanu</span>
</div>
<div class="meta-data--item">
<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon calendar"></div>
<time class="date" pubdate="" datetime="2005-05-23 05:55:00.0">May 23, 2005</time>
</div>
<div class="meta-data--item">
<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon comments"></div>
<a class="comments" data-disqus-identifier="942" href="/blog/2005/05/23/spring-web-flow-pr3-released#disqus_thread">
 </a></div>
</header>
<section class="blog--post desktop-only">
<div><p></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">Spring Web Flow PR3 has been released. Here’s Keith’s mailing list announcement:&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">—&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">Dear Spring Community,</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">I’m pleased to announce the release of Spring Web Flow Preview 3. &nbsp;This is a major new release with a substantial number of new features: both in terms of power and convenience.&nbsp; This release is considered stable for development use.</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">To download, access: <a href="https://sourceforge.net/project/showfiles.php?group_id=73357&amp;package_id=148517"></a><a href="https://sourceforge.net/project/showfiles.php?group_id=73357&amp;package_id=148517">http://sourceforge.net/project/showfiles.php?group_id=73357&amp;package_id=148517</a><br></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">Note: there are a few incompatible changes between PR2 and PR3. &nbsp;For a listing and a porting guide, access the change log here: <a href="https://opensource.atlassian.com/confluence/spring/display/WEBFLOW/Change+Log"></a><a href="https://opensource.atlassian.com/confluence/spring/display/WEBFLOW/Change+Log">http://opensource.atlassian.com/confluence/spring/display/WEBFLOW/Change+Log</a><br></p>
</div>
</section>
